Package: ProteATO
Title: ProteATO App: R Shiny App for the Analysis of Proteomics Data
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("YourFirstName", "YourLastName", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This app is designed to support researchers in interactively exploring and analyzing proteomics data using the DEP workflow. The application provides accessible tools for differential expression analysis, visualization, and biological interpretation of proteomics datasets without requiring advanced R programming skills.
